The open-source [[DIAMETER]] implementation based on RFC 3588 designed by the IETF AAA Working Group. 

The source code of the Open Diameter software is available under the combination of Lesser GNU Public License and GNU Public License. The base protocol implementation is available as a C++ library and  currently supports Linux, BSD and Windows systems.

This implementation is not maintained anymore. 

